{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":349,"text":"I would like to talk to you\nabout why many ehealth projects fail."},{"time":4897,"text":"And I really think\nthat the most important thing of it"},{"time":7642,"text":"is that we stopped listening to patients."},{"time":10590,"text":"And one thing we did at Radboud University"},{"time":12641,"text":"is we appointed a Chief Listening Officer."},{"time":14676,"text":"Not in a very scientific way --"},{"time":16307,"text":"she puts up a little cup\nof coffee or a cup of tea"},{"time":19692,"text":"and asks patients, family, relatives,"},{"time":22359,"text":"\"What's up?"},{"time":23546,"text":"How could we help you?\""},{"time":25463,"text":"And we think, we like to think,"},{"time":27131,"text":"that this is one of the major problems"},{"time":28984,"text":"why all -- maybe not all --"},{"time":31136,"text":"but most of the ehealth projects fail,"},{"time":33000,"text":"since we stopped listening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35206,"text":"This is my weight scale."},{"time":36876,"text":"It's a very simple thing.\nIt's got one knob, on/off."},{"time":40057,"text":"And every morning I hop on it."},{"time":42848,"text":"And yes, I've got a challenge,"},{"time":44799,"text":"as you might see."},{"time":46629,"text":"And I put my challenge on 95 kg."},{"time":49639,"text":"But the thing is that\nit's made this simple"},{"time":52236,"text":"that whenever I hop on,"},{"time":53851,"text":"it sends my data to Google Health as well."},{"time":57291,"text":"And it's collected\nby my general practitioner as well,"},{"time":60577,"text":"so he can see what's my problem in weight,"},{"time":64000,"text":"not on the very moment\nthat I need cardiologic support"},{"time":67701,"text":"or something like it,"},{"time":68916,"text":"but also looking backward."},{"time":71574,"text":"But there's another thing."},{"time":72958,"text":"As some of you might know,"},{"time":74461,"text":"I've got more than 4000\nfollowers on Twitter."},{"time":76811,"text":"So every morning, I hop on my weight scale"},{"time":80453,"text":"and before I'm in my car,"},{"time":81741,"text":"people start talking to me,"},{"time":83074,"text":"\"I think you need\na light lunch today, Lucien.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":85396,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86571,"text":"But that's the nicest thing\nthat could happen,"},{"time":88738,"text":"since this is peer pressure."},{"time":90317,"text":"Peer pressure used to help patients --"},{"time":94001,"text":"since this could be used for obesity,"},{"time":95867,"text":"it could be used\nto stop patients from smoking."},{"time":99484,"text":"But on the other hand,"},{"time":100747,"text":"it also could be used\nto get people out of their chairs"},{"time":104304,"text":"and try to work together\nin some kind of gaming activity"},{"time":107954,"text":"to get more control of their health."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110226,"text":"As of next week,\nit will soon be available,"},{"time":113000,"text":"there will be this little\nblood-pressure meter"},{"time":115338,"text":"connected to an iPhone\nor something or other."},{"time":118580,"text":"And people will be able, from their homes,"},{"time":121352,"text":"to take their blood pressure,"},{"time":122932,"text":"send it to their doctor"},{"time":124645,"text":"and eventually share it\nwith others, for instance,"},{"time":127355,"text":"for over a 100 dollars."},{"time":129286,"text":"And this is the point\nwhere patients get into position"},{"time":132279,"text":"and can collect,\nnot only their own control again,"},{"time":135263,"text":"be captain of their own ship,"},{"time":137208,"text":"but also can help us in health care"},{"time":139549,"text":"due to the challenges that we face,"},{"time":141551,"text":"like health-care cost explosion,"},{"time":144413,"text":"doubled demand and things like that,"},{"time":146284,"text":"make techniques that are easy to use"},{"time":148490,"text":"and start with this\nto embrace patients in the team."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151858,"text":"And you can do this\nwith techniques like this,"},{"time":154143,"text":"but also by crowdsourcing."},{"time":156112,"text":"And one of the things we did,"},{"time":157739,"text":"that I would like to share with you\nintroduced by a little video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161090,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228835,"text":"(Heart-beat)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":233081,"text":"We've all got\nnavigation controls in our car."},{"time":235741,"text":"We maybe even have it in our cellphone."},{"time":238403,"text":"We perfectly know where all the ATMs are,"},{"time":240796,"text":"just about the city of Maastricht."},{"time":242729,"text":"The other thing is we know\nwhere all the gas stations are."},{"time":245789,"text":"And sure, we could find fast food chains."},{"time":248869,"text":"But where would be the nearest AED\nto help this patient?"},{"time":253070,"text":"We asked around, and nobody knew."},{"time":255671,"text":"Nobody knew where\nthe nearest lifesaving AED"},{"time":258606,"text":"was to be obtained right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260686,"text":"So what we did,\nwe crowdsourced the Netherlands."},{"time":263142,"text":"We set up a website, and asked the crowd,"},{"time":265846,"text":"\"If you see an AED, please submit it,"},{"time":268182,"text":"tell us where it is,\ntell us when it's open,\""},{"time":271000,"text":"since sometimes in office hours\nit's closed, of course."},{"time":273986,"text":"And over 10,000 AEDs in the Netherlands"},{"time":276186,"text":"already have been submitted."},{"time":277648,"text":"The next step we took\nwas to find the applications for it."},{"time":280569,"text":"And we built an iPad application."},{"time":282645,"text":"We made an application\nfor Layar: Augmented Reality,"},{"time":285694,"text":"to find these AEDs."},{"time":287462,"text":"And whenever you are\nin a city like Maastricht,"},{"time":289769,"text":"and somebody collapses,\nyou can use your iPhone,"},{"time":292393,"text":"and within the next weeks\nalso your Microsoft cellphone,"},{"time":295963,"text":"to find the nearest AED,"},{"time":297402,"text":"which can save lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299432,"text":"And as of today,"},{"time":300760,"text":"we would like to introduce this,\nnot only as AED4EU,"},{"time":303478,"text":"which is what the product is called,"},{"time":305217,"text":"but also AED4US."},{"time":307000,"text":"And we would like to start this\non a worldwide level."},{"time":309544,"text":"And ask all of our colleagues\nin the rest of the world,"},{"time":312511,"text":"colleague universities, to help us"},{"time":314582,"text":"to find and work and act like a hub"},{"time":317230,"text":"to crowdsource all these AEDs\nall around the world,"},{"time":320584,"text":"that whenever you're on holiday\nand somebody collapses,"},{"time":323573,"text":"might it be your own relative\nor someone just in front of you,"},{"time":327078,"text":"you can find this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328675,"text":"The other thing we would like to ask"},{"time":330414,"text":"is of companies also all over the world"},{"time":332513,"text":"that will be able to help us\nvalidate these AEDs."},{"time":335570,"text":"These might be courier services"},{"time":337412,"text":"or cable guys, for instance,"},{"time":339127,"text":"just to see whether\nthe AED that is submitted"},{"time":341513,"text":"is still in place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343103,"text":"So please help us on this one"},{"time":345000,"text":"and try to make not only\nhealth a little bit better,"},{"time":347976,"text":"but take control of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349168,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350358,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}